Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.16,0:02:05.79,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:121163,125792}Maya unexpectedly received the role of\Nyoung Catherine in "Wuthering Heights",
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.79,0:02:11.84,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:125792,131840}but she struggled to understand\NCatherine's strong love for Heathcliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.84,0:02:16.63,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:131840,136637}One day, she met a lonely\Nyoung boy named Kazu,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.63,0:02:20.09,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:136637,140097}and finally she found\Na way to portray her role.
