Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.77,0:02:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:150775,151942}I'm off to practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.19,0:02:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:155197,158700}Practice?\NIt starts at one o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.09,0:02:58.84,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:176093,178845}Tōyō Theatre Entrance\NAuthorized personnel only
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.01,0:03:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:179012,180638}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.63,0:03:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:180638,183684}Morn—\NWhat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.68,0:03:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:183684,186561}Why's she here at this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.40,0:03:19.32,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:195404,199324}Tōyō Theatre
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.33,0:03:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:211336,213004}I've got no idea what the president was thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:213004,215882}I know, it's his obsession with potential…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.88,0:03:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:215882,219511}That Maya girl doesn't even have\Nanything that shines about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.51,0:03:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:219511,221847}It's impossible to get\Nanything special out of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.76,0:03:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:223765,226268}Well, I guess we just have to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.26,0:03:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:226268,227519}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.18,0:03:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:230188,232023}All right, I'll see you after practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.02,0:03:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:232023,232982}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.98,0:03:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:232982,238155}It's good that Egawa Yuki agreed\Nto be on standby, Mr. Sawaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.15,0:04:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:238155,240866}She's just right for Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.86,0:04:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:240866,244661}I agree. If Kitajima Maya doesn't do well, then…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.66,0:04:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:244661,247539}Exactly. She's bound to make lots of mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.42,0:04:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:259426,263096}Let's start the scene\Nwith young Catherine and Heathcliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.09,0:04:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:263096,264014}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.98,0:04:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:273982,275859}No, let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.85,0:04:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:275859,279029}Now that our father is dead,\NI'm the man of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.02,0:04:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:279029,281573}Heathcliff will be treated\Nas a servant from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.57,0:04:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:281573,284516}Do you understand, Catherine?\NI won't allow you to play with a servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:284516,285869}No, let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.86,0:04:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:285869,289456}I won't stop being close to Heathcliff,\Nno matter what you say!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.45,0:04:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:289456,291500}I love Heathcliff!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.50,0:04:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:291500,292334}Catherine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.33,0:04:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:292334,295796}Don't go, Heathcliff!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.79,0:04:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:295796,296922}Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.13,0:04:59.04,Retrospective,,0,0,0,,{TIME:297130,299049}Don't go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.63,0:05:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:304638,306389}Heathcliff!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:322113,323865}Hmm, she's pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.86,0:05:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:323865,326743}These young ones are gonna\Nkeep us adults on our toes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.45,0:05:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:327452,330038}Hey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.03,0:05:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:330038,332582}Ouch, she bit me for real!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.12,0:05:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:334125,338839}All right, all right, enough of the\Nlove scenes. Give me some attention too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.83,0:05:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:338839,341091}Oh, what did I—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.09,0:05:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:341091,343176}Look at this bite mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.67,0:05:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:344678,346721}Oh, I'm sorry, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.68,0:05:50.22,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:348682,350225}What a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.22,0:05:54.97,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:350225,354979}Her passion, her wildness…\NI was taken by her acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.64,0:05:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:356647,359025}I hope you'll like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.48,0:06:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:363488,364906}I knitted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.90,0:06:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:364906,366616}It took me a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.61,0:06:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:366616,369578}You can wear this all the time,\Neven when I'm not around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.57,0:06:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:369578,370996}Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.83,0:06:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:373832,376501}I know you, Ryo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.50,0:06:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:376501,378295}That girl, Kitajima Maya…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.29,0:06:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:378295,382173}She's the one who's on your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.17,0:06:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:382173,385551}I know it.\NI know everything about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.55,0:06:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:385551,387762}Tell me, Ryo, what's so attractive about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.76,0:06:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:387762,389764}She's so plain and rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.76,0:06:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:389764,392601}Forget about the play\Nfor a moment and talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.56,0:06:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:394561,396604}I'm prettier than she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:396604,399316}I'm a better actress than she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.31,0:06:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:399316,403528}She only got the role because because\Nthe president's interested in her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.52,0:06:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:403528,406990}She's gonna mess up soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.99,0:06:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:406990,410201}Then I'll get to be Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:410201,412454}Hey, Ryo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.45,0:06:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:412454,414497}Why don't you shut up\Nfor a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.62,0:07:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:427626,428385}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.09,0:07:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:430096,432641}Sakurakōji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.64,0:07:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:432641,434867}I stopped by your apartment,\Nthey told me you'd be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.86,0:07:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:434867,437187}Here, eat this before it gets cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.77,0:07:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:437771,438729}Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.15,0:07:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:443151,444945}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.94,0:07:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:444945,446613}This is delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.65,0:07:31.15,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:449658,451159}Gift{NOTE:御見舞}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.57,0:07:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:451575,454319}I'm impressed with your guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.31,0:07:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:454319,455372}Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.37,0:07:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:455372,458208}To come and see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.20,0:07:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:458208,462128}I'm seriously concerned\Nabout your health, Miss Tsukikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.12,0:07:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:462128,466340}As long as "The Crimson Goddess"\Nremains in my possession, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.72,0:07:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:471721,474474}Go ahead and take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.47,0:07:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:474474,479145}A cold and cruel person like you\Nmust have many ways, Mr. Masumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.01,0:08:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:480012,484401}I want to acquire it legitimately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:484401,485402}One day I'll succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:496830,499498}You're playing Catherine?\NThat's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.49,0:08:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:499498,500333}Hey, here's an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.33,0:08:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:500333,504254}Could you read Heathcliff's lines for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.25,0:08:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:504254,506840}It's hard to get the feel for it all by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.84,0:08:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:506840,509717}I get to play your boyfriend?\NAll right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.26,0:08:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:515265,519810}They said we can't play\Nwith each other, but we sneak out…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.10,0:08:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:523106,525275}And here we are, Heathcliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.27,0:08:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:525275,527318}I hope my brother doesn't catch us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.15,0:08:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:529154,533408}D-don't worry. If he comes,\Nthen I'll hit him good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.40,0:08:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:533408,535035}Don't go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.03,0:08:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:535035,537996}Stay by my side forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.99,0:09:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:537996,541640}Please stay with me forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.64,0:09:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:541640,543752}If you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.54,0:09:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:544544,547297}I am you, and you are me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.29,0:09:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:547297,550633}We are united as one soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.63,0:09:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:550633,554137}Promise me that we will stay\Nthe same when we're older.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.13,0:09:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:554137,557265}Your real father is an emperor of China,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.26,0:09:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:557265,559559}and your real mother is a queen of India.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:559559,564814}You'll leave here someday,\Nget rich, and come back to get me…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.81,0:09:27.15,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:564814,567150}You are not looking at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.15,0:09:30.98,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:567150,570987}The person in your eyes is not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.98,0:09:34.15,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:570987,574157}The person you're in love with is Heathcliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.15,0:09:35.07,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:574157,575074}I wonder if…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.08,0:09:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:581081,582165}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.16,0:09:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:582165,584959}I… I'm not Heathcliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.95,0:09:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:584959,588338}I don't want to be\Na substitute or a shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.75,0:09:56.32,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:593759,596328}Sakurakōji, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:09:57.88,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:596328,597889}Why are you upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.56,0:10:14.53,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:612569,614531}Cafe Bidoro
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.07,0:10:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:618076,620252}Here, cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.25,0:10:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:620252,624332}But, Sakurakōji was…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.33,0:10:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:624332,627085}Things will go back to normal soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.08,0:10:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:627085,628711}But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.71,0:10:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:628711,634968}How about sending him a ticket\Nfor the premiere of "Wuthering Heights"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.09,0:10:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:636094,636678}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.34,0:10:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:638346,642016}You only need to concentrate\Non Catherine right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.01,0:10:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:642016,645611}Let Sakurakōji see your wonderful Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.97,0:10:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:645979,647230}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.39,0:10:50.35,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:646396,650358}Tōyō Theatre
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.94,0:10:53.11,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:650942,653111}As the opening day approached,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.11,0:10:58.49,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:653111,658491}the synergy between Maya and Ryo,\Nand Kagawa and Natsu intensified.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.07,0:11:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:660076,663079}Catherine, we'll stay together forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.07,0:11:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:663079,665415}I am you, and you are me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:665415,668293}We are united as one soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.29,0:11:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:668293,669586}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.25,0:11:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:671254,675466}Mr. Majima's words sound so real lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.46,0:11:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:675466,677552}I wonder if they're actually in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.55,0:11:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:677552,679137}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.80,0:11:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:679804,681305}Heathcliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.84,0:11:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:682849,684892}We'll be together forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.97,0:11:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:685977,687228}Forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.62,0:11:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:703620,709041}– Great work.\N– Good bye.  – Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.92,0:11:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:714923,717383}Maya, let's walk home together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:11:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:718150,719510}C-Chilly…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.51,0:12:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:719510,720762}It is chilly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:720762,722764}Oh yeah, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.43,0:12:09.18,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:727435,729187}That's my present!
Comment: 0,0:12:20.69,0:12:20.69,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:740698,740698}Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:12:24.49,0:12:24.49,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:744493,744493}#Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:12:27.45,0:12:27.45,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:747454,747454}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.53,0:12:32.46,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:747538,752460}{\1c&H101010&\3c&H101010&\4c&H101010&\t(0,1500,\1c&HE4F0CB&\3c&H24320A&\4c&H202020&)}Tōyō Theatre
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.54,0:12:36.67,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:753544,756673}Today is the premiere of "Wuthering Heights".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.80,0:12:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:766808,770728}This hall is huge.\NMy heart's beating so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.98,0:12:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:772981,775775}I wonder if Maya's gonna be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.77,0:13:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:775775,780613}She'll be fine. Once she's on stage,\Nnothing can stop her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.61,0:13:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:780613,782156}I'm kind of anxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.15,0:13:09.70,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:785159,789706}Catherine Earnshaw…\NNow I'll wear your mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.70,0:13:12.62,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:789706,792625}We will be as one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:17.50,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:792625,797505}Miss Tsukikage,\NMr. Purple Rose, Sakurakōji…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:18.54,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:797505,798548}Please watch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.13,0:13:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:800132,801384}He isn't here…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.38,0:13:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:801384,804137}What's wrong?\NLooking for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.13,0:13:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:804137,808141}That seat's reserved for Sakurakōji.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.14,0:13:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:808141,810518}Oh, Maya's boyfriend…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.51,0:13:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:810518,812353}The play's about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:812353,814446}He'll show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.44,0:13:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:814446,815898}I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.36,0:13:47.82,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:825366,827827}Maya's rival, Himekawa Ayumi was present.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.82,0:13:51.41,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:827827,831414}Yuki, who passionately loved Majima Ryo,\Nwas there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.12,0:13:58.29,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:836127,838296}Calm down.\NI'm Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.29,0:14:00.34,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:838296,840340}I love Heathcliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.34,0:14:04.88,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:840340,844886}Just like Kazu, if Heathcliff is gone,\Nthen I'll be all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.88,0:14:06.09,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:844886,846095}I don't want to be alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.43,0:14:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:856439,857857}Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.32,0:14:25.32,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:863320,865323}Let's do our best, Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.53,0:14:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:866532,868201}Get ready, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.46,0:14:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:881464,882507}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.50,0:14:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:882507,884425}You want me to get along\Nwith Heathcliff?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.42,0:14:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:884425,885801}Hell no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.89,0:15:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:898898,901025}You are so patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.40,0:15:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:902401,905446}Hmph, I'll kick him out\Nof the Heights someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.99,0:15:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:908991,913996}Wearing my shoes, wearing my clothes…\NWho do you think you are!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.37,0:15:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:914372,916958}Don't!\NDon't, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.95,0:15:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:916958,920052}Heathcliff has done nothing wrong!\NNothing wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.05,0:15:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:920052,921045}Get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.04,0:15:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:921045,922713}How dare you touch Catherine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.06,0:15:44.73,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:938062,944735}With his passionate acting, the actor\Nfor Hindley had cut Majima Ryo's lip.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.73,0:15:49.49,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:944735,949490}This accident was about to cause\Na problem for the flow of the play.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.94,0:15:52.86,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:949949,952869}I have to do something.\NI have to help Heathcliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.86,0:15:56.28,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:952869,956289}W-What would Heathcliff do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.28,0:15:57.83,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:956289,957832}What would Catherine do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.05,0:16:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:969051,970595}You are so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.55,0:16:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:971554,974640}Even when you're bleeding,\Nyou don't even complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.64,0:16:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:974640,976058}I love that about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.52,0:16:20.35,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:979520,980353}Maya…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.81,0:16:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:984817,986319}Let's go, Heathcliff!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.31,0:16:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:986319,988571}Try to catch me. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.57,0:16:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:988571,991491}Come on, hurry!\NTry to catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.82,0:16:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:993826,997288}Catherine, you are the only person\NI love in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.28,0:16:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:997288,1002084}You love me,\Nmy everything, my soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.08,0:16:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1002084,1004879}What were you thinking,\Nripping your costume like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.88,0:16:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1005880,1007840}Catherine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.25,0:16:51.59,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1010258,1011593}That kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.59,0:16:55.38,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1011593,1015389}To be able to do that\Nin a blink of an eye, you must love Majima.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.38,0:16:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1015389,1016641}Here, hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.22,0:16:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1017224,1018351}I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.39,0:17:06.44,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1020394,1026442}Despite the feelings of Yuki and Sakurakōji, who\Nrefused to believe Maya and Ryo were in love,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.44,0:17:09.57,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1026442,1029570}the love between Heathcliff and Catherine\Nwas getting more and more passionate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.06,0:17:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1030062,1031030}Heathcliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.70,0:17:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1040706,1042041}Those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.04,0:17:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1042041,1045086}I hope they didn't forget their words.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.08,0:17:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1045086,1049915}Look at them, even when they're silent\Nthe audience's attention never wavers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.91,0:17:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1049915,1051509}What a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.09,0:17:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052093,1054095}Now, let's go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.09,0:17:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1054095,1055680}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.10,0:17:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1061102,1063646}We finally ran away, Heathcliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.64,0:17:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063646,1065439}I hope my brother doesn't catch us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.02,0:17:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066023,1069318}Don't worry. If he comes,\Nthen I'll hit him good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.31,0:17:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1069318,1070903}Don't go anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.37,0:17:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072371,1074282}Those eyes…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.28,0:17:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1074282,1076701}You are me, and I am you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.70,0:17:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1076701,1079453}We are united as one soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.45,0:18:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1079453,1082582}Promise me that\Nwe won't change when we grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.58,0:18:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082582,1084041}Yes, Heathcliff!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.25,0:18:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086252,1087753}Mr. Hayami.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.75,0:18:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1087753,1088421}Let's talk
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.26,0:18:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1094260,1098639}If you love her, then watch until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.63,0:18:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098639,1101559}I love her. That's why\NI can't watch anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.55,0:18:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1101559,1102810}Go back to your seat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.81,0:18:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1102810,1107315}You, you'll never understand how I feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.31,0:18:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1107315,1108858}Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.74,0:18:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1111744,1115114}As long as you live here,\NI'll stay here in the Heights.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.11,0:18:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1115114,1116782}I'll put up with anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.70,0:18:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119702,1122788}Heathcliff, we'll be together forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.25,0:18:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1134258,1136302}It's our turn now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.59,0:18:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137595,1139263}Kind of awkward to go out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.26,0:19:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1139263,1143601}We are better-known actors and our scenes\Nare longer, but I don't feel so confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.60,0:19:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143601,1145519}Come on, we're the main roles here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.51,0:19:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1145519,1147062}We can't let her steal the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.14,0:19:08.06,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1146145,1148064}Dressing room
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.19,0:19:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1157198,1159617}I wonder if Sakurakōji was watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.53,0:19:30.33,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1164538,1170336}Natsu Eriko and Kagawa Hideaki\Nperformed very well too,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.33,0:19:34.09,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1170336,1174090}and "Wuthering Heights" ended up\Nhaving a very successful premiere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.08,0:19:53.98,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190089,1193984}Sakurakōji… I told him to wait here in the letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.61,0:20:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200616,1202868}Are you looking for Heathcliff, Catherine?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.57,0:20:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1204578,1206163}You did really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.74,0:20:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1208749,1211836}Passionate and wild Catherine…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.83,0:20:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1211836,1214338}Yes, that was true, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.00,0:20:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1219009,1223222}It was sort of like a little child\Nwhose toy was taken away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.22,0:20:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1223222,1226225}Not the kind of passionate love for a lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.89,0:20:30.89,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1227893,1230896}Not a passionate love for a lover?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.15,0:20:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1234150,1237319}Seems like you have much more\Nto learn about acting out love, little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.28,0:20:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1240281,1243909}Hurry and grow up, little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.90,0:20:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1243909,1246036}My name is not "little girl"!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:20:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1256005,1256714}Huh…?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.54,0:20:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1257548,1259925}How was Kitajima Maya?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.92,0:21:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1259925,1263387}Was she playing Catherine in love well?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.38,0:21:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1263387,1266599}She doesn't know real love yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.51,0:21:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1269518,1271353}Mr. Majima was so great!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.35,0:21:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1271353,1273189}I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.35,0:21:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1277359,1279445}Hey, Maya. I'll take you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.19,0:21:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1282198,1282948}Ryo…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.40,0:21:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1284408,1285409}I was waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.53,0:21:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1286535,1288370}You can give me a ride home, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.34,0:21:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1308349,1311894}Kitajima Maya, Kitajima Maya.\NThere's a phone call for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.89,0:21:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1311894,1314355}Oh, that might be Sakurakōji!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.89,0:21:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1315898,1317608}Hi, this is Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.60,0:21:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1317608,1318484}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.11,0:22:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1321110,1322488}What are you saying, Rei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.48,0:22:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1322488,1324031}You're not serious, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.79,0:22:09.11,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1326792,1329119}Miss Tsukikage is about to pass away?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.11,0:22:12.45,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1329119,1332456}Don't die! Please, don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.38,0:22:31.39,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1347388,1351392}You promised me that you wouldn't die\Nuntil you direct "The Crimson Goddess".
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.39,0:22:33.72,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1351392,1353726}Don't give in to the illness.\NDon't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.72,0:22:35.22,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1353726,1355229}Operating room in use
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.61,0:22:44.98,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1362611,1364989}No… No!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.98,0:22:48.40,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1364989,1368409}Don't die!\NTeacher!
